{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01CKa645hu4RU6DGASZwkpbX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fixed issue #5 — added upload progress indicator and file size validation:\n\n**Backend:**\n- Added `GET /api/limits` endpoint returning `max_upload_bytes` (500MB) and `supported_formats`\n- Extracted `MAX_UPLOAD_BYTES` constant used by both the limits endpoint and body limit layer\n\n**Frontend:**\n- Replaced `fetch` with `XMLHttpRequest` in `uploadFile` for upload progress tracking\n- Added `onProgress` callback parameter to `uploadFile`\n- Added client-side file size validation before upload starts (rejects with clear error message)\n- Added animated progress bar in the upload drop zone during upload\n- Shows max file size hint (\"Max 500.0 MB\") in the upload area\n\n```\n---RALPH_STATUS---\nSTATUS: COMPLETE\nTASKS_COMPLETED_THIS_LOOP: 1\nFILES_MODIFIED: 3\nTESTS_STATUS: PASSING\nWORK_TYPE: IMPLEMENTATION\nEXIT_SIGNAL: false\nRECOMMENDATION: Next task: #10 - Display verification results and quality scores in GUI\n---END_RALPH_STATUS---\n```"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":297,"cache_read_input_tokens":152841,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":297},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c9bd7957-c8f2-4e48-8fcc-7059d242854c","uuid":"ed025685-a1b0-45dc-bb31-7c449356c206"}
